\c 23
\s Jehovha mufudzi wangu
\d Pisarema raDhavhidhi.
\p
\v 1 Jehovha ndiye mufudzi wangu; hapana chandingashaiwa.
\v 2 Anondivatisa pasi pamafuro manyoro; anondisesedza pamvura inozorodza.
\v 3 Anoponesa mweya wangu; anondifambisa panzira dzokururama nokuda kwezita rake.
\v 4 Zvirokwazvo, kunyange ndikafamba mumupata womumvuri worufu, handingatongotyi zvakaipa; nokuti imwi muneni; tsvimbo yenyu nomudonzvo wenyu zvinondinyaradza.
\v 5 Munondigadzirira chokudya pamberi pavadzivisi vangu; makazodza musoro wangu namafuta; mukombe wangu unopfachuka.
\v 6 Zvirokwazvo unyoro nenyasha zvichanditevera mazuva ese oupenyu hwangu; ini ndichagara mumba maJehovha mazuva namazuva.
